#include<stdio.h>
#define max(a,b) a>b?a:b
#define min(a,b) a>b?b:a
int main()
{
    int test;
    scanf("%d",&test);
    for(int t=0;t<test;t++)
    {
            int x0[2],x1[2],y0[2],y1[2];
            for(int j=0;j<2;j++)
            scanf("%d %d %d %d",&x0[j],&y0[j],&x1[j],&y1[j]);
            if(x1[0]<=x0[1]||x0[0]>=x1[1]||y1[0]<=y0[1]||y0[0]>=y1[1])
            printf("No Overlap\n");
            else
            printf("%d %d %d %d\n",max(x0[0],x0[1]),max(y0[0],y0[1]),min(x1[0],x1[1]),min(y1[0],y1[1]));
    }
}
